{"id": 1121, "genre": 1001, "title": "你是如何扮演城市空巢青年的？", "description": "一个人住间30平出租屋，对象暂无，感到最治愈的地方是便利店，是我，一个当代空巢青年。", "record_count": 7999, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160716121443eX1NAWdjI4ShFHKO.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-29T17:00:14Z", "options": [{"id": 103425, "content": "要瘫倒在沙发上。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698138}, {"id": 102915, "content": "总想做点什么，然后睡着了", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696276}, {"id": 103429, "content": "小编，虽然我也喜欢全家，但请问你们收了多少钱广告费？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698157}, {"id": 103430, "content": "感觉身体被掏空......", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482523}, {"id": 102921, "content": "想看书却刷起了好奇心日报", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162386}, {"id": 102924, "content": "躺床上玩手机一整天", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696813}, {"id": 103190, "content": "追剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 623377}, {"id": 103195, "content": "发呆?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697482}, {"id": 108288, "content": "电视机开着不是为了看电视 纯粹让家里有点声音", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117813}, {"id": 103169, "content": "看完美剧英剧日剧就手足无措了，然后开始怀疑人生，直到有不想活了的冲动。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697443}, {"id": 103171, "content": "我好寂寞，好孤独，好无助，好悲伤…听着李志感觉这世界不会好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 105386}, {"id": 102916, "content": "看韩剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 630150}, {"id": 102917, "content": "对着电脑发呆", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654307}, {"id": 102919, "content": "根本不需要扮演", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436982}, {"id": 105223, "content": "每天犹豫是自己做的还是叫外卖。在纠结中度过每一天", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 121153}, {"id": 102920, "content": "我只是学到了原来红包还可以发给电脑传输助手.....orz", "image": null, "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635240}, {"id": 103176, "content": "看直播", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252407}, {"id": 103432, "content": "不满意现在的状态，拼命工作，依旧没办法改变现在的状态，傻傻的一个人循环着。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678284}, {"id": 102922, "content": "全家是我家～", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162124}, {"id": 103434, "content": "拿起手机打开微信，刷刷朋友圈点个赞，看看今天有什么事情发生", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697223}, {"id": 103179, "content": "今天是星期几？？？算了，星期几都没关系了-_-#", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667933}, {"id": 103180, "content": "在家睡了一天。赶在超市打烊前觅食。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659306}, {"id": 103437, "content": "APP试玩兼职加微ty-562027250\n零投入纯收入，苹果设备一个APP奖励1-4元，安卓0.5-1元，现结随时提现，适合长期做，想赚零花钱生活费的来吧", "image": "img/option/option/20160731172418GQgWNb6cD1Y3nL0a.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698151}, {"id": 102926, "content": "在PAD电影的声音陪伴下，画DIY 数字油画，为什么总是冒出来已经画完数字的另一个部分？", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696801}, {"id": 103182, "content": "难以早睡。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 476254}, {"id": 102927, "content": "一直烦躁总觉得该做点什么却不知道该做什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696821}, {"id": 103440, "content": "早起买个菜，打扫下卫生，瘫在床上，煲电视剧。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698174}, {"id": 102929, "content": "额(⊙o⊙)…，一天追完7季的美剧，一整季的综艺节目，。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696823}, {"id": 102930, "content": "很少回家，公司事多，有一大堆文件没批完。所以经常住办公室", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686444}, {"id": 112659, "content": "偶尔会担心意外猝死啥的没人发现", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 361532}, {"id": 103444, "content": "嗷，我不是空巢青年哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698152}, {"id": 98581, "content": "外卖红包多到不好意思群发，发给文件传输助手自己领一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 1068, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 102933, "content": "感觉这才是真实的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 553535}, {"id": 102934, "content": "没什么兴趣爱好，坐在电脑前不知道干嘛，躺床上也不知道干嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686056}, {"id": 103446, "content": "不恋爱，不结婚，放纵不羁，自由一生", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698189}, {"id": 98583, "content": "妆不大会化，衣服也不大会挑，但网络、灯和水管什么的，修得不错。", "image": null, "praise_count": 449, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 102935, "content": "感觉死在屋里都不会有人发现…", "image": null, "praise_count": 139, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 626289}, {"id": 102936, "content": "说好要做页面的……结果刚醒…加油 TAT~", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493672}, {"id": 98585, "content": "出门丢垃圾忘带钥匙，在寒风中颤抖着等开锁匠七八回了", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 98587, "content": "晚睡的时候还挺希望有人来骂自己一下——“还不睡觉作啥妖呢”", "image": null, "praise_count": 228, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 102939, "content": "一个人在家做清洁，累到睡2甜", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 518054}, {"id": 102940, "content": "玩一天的电脑，睡到中午12点", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696884}, {"id": 102941, "content": "好想全世界的人一起宅", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696847}, {"id": 102942, "content": "周末穿的最多的是拖鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684884}, {"id": 102943, "content": "我感觉自己就是这样的，说出了好多人的心声啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685191}, {"id": 103199, "content": "刷动漫，自己做饭吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674953}, {"id": 102945, "content": "孤单寂寞冷啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685191}, {"id": 104737, "content": "待在员工寝室看书，做20个仰卧起坐，外加10个俯卧撑。发呆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704643}, {"id": 102947, "content": "无聊时看一整天美剧，梦中发现还可以有“她”陪伴", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696973}, {"id": 103459, "content": "关于家里的各种电器啊什么的修理的还不错？?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658150}]}